{"tid":1515712,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"統計一下多唔多人用auto start stop","createTime":"2019-08-29T09:35:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T04:52:26.000Z","uid":92645,"like":54,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"f27088538e402644a1fa34fd0377385a435c319a","tid":1515712,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無用 怕傷偈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用auto start stop 慳油！<br />\n<br />\n我就無用，停燈位同我stop都仲好，但塞車/排紅隧之類既 stop and go traffic都同我又開又熄，真係好煩"},{"pid":"2c3682a66401c7a9b995e0c08173b76bb4cf31f4","tid":1515712,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:35:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a6f0391337ad0c4c0d4b09bbcfff7ab546feac47","tid":1515712,"uid":196924,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:39:19.000Z","msg":"喺香港呢啲分秒必爭嘅地方<br />\n用auto start stop就注定你起步永遠輸俾DC9"},{"pid":"9c706783c109319b6ace1d58fb5d9729dda597d1","tid":1515712,"uid":65470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T10:27:57.000Z","msg":"自己部車無<br />\n個FD部車有 已篤電腦auto off<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602df4c0c8de1c6d4d26f6b18494fb71e636312b","tid":1515712,"uid":46033,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:08:46.000Z","msg":"唔好ON9 , 必定關既功能,  香港行行停停, 佢熄熄著著, D死人聲煩死人<br />\n仲要斷冷氣壓縮機, 只得吹風, 夏天死緊"},{"pid":"14ba409bf26e085865605066a57a47525fe6e3c9","tid":1515712,"uid":22402,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T09:04:06.000Z","msg":"個frd用得太多 副偈磨到蝕咗<br />\n返benz原廠整咗十零萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 嚇到我都唔敢再用auto start stop<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"811098d09b8c5a4197780b20c0375c3ce35447f2","tid":1515712,"uid":269954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f27088538e402644a1fa34fd0377385a435c319a","tid":1515712,"uid":92645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T09:35:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無用 怕傷偈<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有用auto start stop 慳油！<br />\n<br />\n我就無用，停燈位同我stop都仲好，但塞車/排紅隧之類既 stop and go traffic都同我又開又熄，真係好煩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:21:35.000Z","msg":"新車嗰陣有用，個油耗數字係會靚仔好多。之後發覺佢成日喺架車未停定(可能車速得返 5 km/h) 就 off 咗 engine ，變咗臨到燈口停得好 chok ，本身我揸慣溫柔落 brake 慢慢停。然後發現慳到嘅油耗值好少錢，所以而家每次著車都慣左熄 auto start/stop"},{"pid":"b129e59720abd37d6c8eda6fe2787b3a6fd1b4fe","tid":1515712,"uid":8997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T11:49:19.000Z","msg":"一開車第一件事就係熄咗佢"},{"pid":"1f5e38d81e42fb7a8633b2f79a431c4c483c499d","tid":1515712,"uid":134375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:01:20.000Z","msg":"利申我連auto hold都覺得好麻煩，<br />\n係塞車踩break未停定已經幫我hold住個break，<br />\n然後燈位又要比油先行，冇左果種torque convert果種鬆break向直推果下好唔習慣，<br />\n所以唔洗點講auto start stop，個人覺得大家都係麻煩野。"},{"pid":"5cac3a97689c1cdc5be383c3b45683a768b16585","tid":1515712,"uid":203794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:07:17.000Z","msg":"之前試過唔熄 有一次出路口 佢自己stop完之後start唔返 死咗火<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2013 Nissan Serena Highway Star(行貨)"},{"pid":"43e808c93816a764678190084785cb76d53c72d7","tid":1515712,"uid":55125,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T14:08:24.000Z","msg":"你問我就好傳統既人黎<br />\n咩auto hold start stop 甚至電子手制 <br />\n一個都唔想要<br />\nAuto hold 短就踩實一陣冼死 長就拉手制啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢同你hold搞到 要就住深淺踩<br />\nStart stop 直頭多魚 香港九成時間開冷氣 <br />\n佢熄一陣就開返 佢熱一熱 冷氣又要谷大小小去涼返        油又唔係真係慳好多<br />\n電子手制純粹我個人覺在就唔實在 無左拉威也聲 <br />\n可惜 新車 全部都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d3659a1b317d5797f93cd7ea76bb1cff257d7ed","tid":1515712,"uid":12275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:29:40.000Z","msg":"起步重新著車個下真係好令人煩厭<br />\n無左揸車個種流暢感<br />\n對start stop 功能十分反感<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7faf6975118146368e551da05a02f097c1216b0","tid":1515712,"uid":38440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T04:52:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}